+ Parameters

    + ehrId (string) - EHR id
    + versionedObjectUid (string) - VERSIONED_COMPOSITION's uid
    + versionSelector (string, optional) - version time specifier

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /ehrs/{ehrId}/versioned_compositions/{versionedObjectUid}/versions/{versionUid}
