    + Body

            {
                "contribution": {},
                "signature": "...",
                "commit_audit": {},
                "uid": "...",
                "data": {
                    "_type": "COMPOSITION",
                    "name": {
                        "_type": "DV_TEXT",
                        "value": "Vital Signs"
                    }
                    ...
                }
            }

+ Response 404

    No no VERSIONED_COMPOSITION with uid or no version with versionUid.

    + Body
